latestPosts.caption:
If you’re dealing with fungal acne or constant breakouts, your moisturizer might be part of the problem.
I’ve seen this happen too often — wrong formulas, clogged pores, more irritation.

This one’s different.
I trust it. I recommend it.

Consultation Diaries Episode 2: Uneven skin tan

Sun was fun... until your face is two shades darker than your neck 👀
If your skin looks patchy, inflamed or just off, don’t panic or bleach it.

✅ Gentle exfoliation + barrier repair
✅ Skin-brightening actives (niacinamide, kojic, vitamin C)
✅ SPF 50 every day, especially on the neck, arms & hands

💡 Tan doesn’t need panic. It needs patience + the right plan.
Swipe ➡️ for the full routine
